WEBVTT

00:00:00.060 --> 00:00:02.730
Hello humans, it is I, Bucky.

00:00:02.780 --> 00:00:06.000
Please buy as much as you<br>can from my online store,

00:00:06.050 --> 00:00:09.220
so I can afford to fight<br>these pesky murder charges.

00:00:09.290 --> 00:00:10.440
You know how it is!

00:00:10.514 --> 00:00:12.494
 One day you're at the Sainsbury's

00:00:12.584 --> 00:00:14.654
and the next you're burying your colleague.

00:00:14.744 --> 00:00:16.964
I never liked his jokes anyway.

00:00:17.064 --> 00:00:18.874
Thanks for your support,

00:00:18.944 --> 00:00:22.484
it's surprisingly hard to find a<br>lawyer to represent a robot.